As part of the news, Jack will get to remove his chemo-port and hopefully start getting to be a normal kid again. He has been a trooper through all of this, and I have been very impressed with his ability to deal with his newfound fame. Above all else, he and his foundation have targeted a goal of $1 Million in research fundraising for 2013, which shows that this is so much bigger than one kid.
